Insight on Leadership: Service, Stewardship, Spirit, and Servant Leadership

$45.00






This second collection of essays on the meaning and practice of servant-leadership picks up where Reflections on Leadership left off. In the process it projects the evolutionary growth of the servant-as-leader idea into the 21st century. 


